{"title":"Moxifloxacino","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Moxifloxacino-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Moxifloxacino","guid":"Dprv-Jh6A1ud41heZVURzg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Uso y\\NDosificación:","guid":"KwljzmX8QAcd0t2U1TUeag","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• FQ: Amplio espectro, incluye patógenos respiratorios y entéricos.","guid":"LF3cjhnC0X5DhuBxz13TRw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Anaerobios: Alta actividad vs. 87% de patógenos anaerobios (peritonitis) (Clin Infect Dis, 2011).","guid":"WSmt0GVz2VxOXVX4z26PeQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• N. gonorrhoeae: No recomendado por CDC (MMWR, 2007).","guid":"d1A2Rr72UX3xHBtJgc2gYA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• M. tuberculosis: Terapia de segunda línea (no aprobada por FDA). ↓ Niveles con Rifampina (Clin Infect Dis, 2007).","guid":"pfjTljFAWtJAsnWqYIOGXg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Administración oral: 4h antes o 8h después de antiácidos, sucralfato, hierro, multivitamínicos con zinc. Calcio ↔ moxifloxacino insignificante.","guid":"4lA7VNL-JmoB-NHZzQRj6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Dosis en\\NAdultos:","guid":"XERWEwz42yPaQQWWmRv2Mw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• General: 400 mg po/IV q24h.","guid":"6PL9kh1wyAtJbRdAIQQtzQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Conjuntivitis bacteriana: 1 gota en ojo afectado tid x7 días.","guid":"JrD0vvzeNyDKl3w_bPEXbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"Dosis Pediátrica\\N(>28 días):","guid":"b2sHOA7p0riexVUHHpjhUw","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Seguridad y eficacia\\Nno establecida.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"Ajustes Renales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• CrCl o eGFR: Sin ajuste.","guid":"1yjEPML7XUpLS3e8t-mEPQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Hemodiálisis, CAPD, CRRT, SLED: Sin ajuste.","guid":"nSumKK1y5hA9t7Qfa-mLog","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Ajustes Hepáticos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Ninguno.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\NAdversos:","guid":"SuA1ssw7LPTpvXB4S1Vv0w","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• General: 3.8% suspensión por efectos adversos.","guid":"xxbFCAbHz86sMDRqqAiv0A","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Frecuentes: Náuseas (7%), vómitos (2%), cefalea (2%).","guid":"vmMDBDNH2hM64Gz4xo7pWg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Raros: Rash, fotosensibilidad, confusión, disritmias.","guid":"nPSeuvCRTlzISqunR6M_og","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"• FQ y miastenia gravis: Posible exacerbación de debilidad muscular.","guid":"p_UpMftV4vCgyRLxBU5_NQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Riesgo en\\NEmbarazo:","guid":"8TBnmQtfV8ETfSeO-yym6g","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Categoría C (FDA).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Lactancia: Uso a corto plazo seguro, monitorizar toxicidad GI en el lactante.","guid":"1593KzXyFbU-kb2mVE_UMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Espectro\\NAntimicrobiano","guid":"E2IOBgeqOiJ6i-hujXIY2g","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"RECOMENDADO ++ (3)","guid":"kXYM6X5ohH4GQqx1VCkcBw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• H. influenzae","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Legionella sp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• M. pneumoniae","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"ACTIVO + (34)  ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Aeromonas sp.  • Arcanobacter sp.  • C. burnetii  • C. freundii  • C. jejuni  • C. koseri  • C. trachomatis  •\\NChlamydophila sp.  • E. cloacae  • E. coli (S)  • E. faecalis (VS)  • K. aerogenes  • K. oxytoca (S)  • K. pneumoniae (S)  • L.\\Nmonocytogenes  • Leptospira sp.  • M. catarrhalis  • P. mirabilis  • P. multocida  • P. vulgaris  • Peptostreptococci  • Prevotella sp.  •\\NProvidencia sp.  • S. aureus (MSSA)  • S. epidermidis (MS)  • S. lugdunensis  • S. saprophyticus  • Salmonella sp.  • Serratia\\Nmarcescens  • Shigella sp.  • Staph coag-neg (MS)  • Strep. pneumoniae  • Viridans Strep.  • Y. enterocolitica","guid":"otrFv2xC9MQiP2JgQqErpA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"PK/PD Índice:","guid":"FAi6Cw5nsoIX41RdoX30UA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• AUC/MIC 24h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Preparaciones Farmacéuticas:","guid":"jiqUCoBkkcY4EZdYrxQAKA","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Tab (400 mg), Inyección, Solución oftálmica 0.5%","guid":"SBNNpuITxlhPzwb03Vjr2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"Absorción Oral (%):","guid":"v34Fsla-ky-7JRFzEi2fGQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• 89%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"32","text":"Tmax (hr):","guid":"H9xMiKt_IWrqXkHe4Aev6w","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• po: 1-3 h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"Concentración Sérica Máxima (µg/mL):","guid":"KxPL38ejx_qTM8T2pdU0jg","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• 4.2-4.6 (400 mg po/IV q24h, SS)","guid":"kg02c-eUTseNLqAReSssSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"32","text":"Unión a Proteínas (%):","guid":"4X2H2xSOtF6c4RjiQ90olA","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• 30-50%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"32","text":"Volumen de Distribución (Vd):","guid":"lMYixe_UKaplvfQJdj_vLw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• 2.2 L/kg","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"32","text":"T½ Sérica Promedio (hr):","guid":"FIRMB3tJvcuy3egHM3gQbw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• 10-14 h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"32","text":"Eliminación:","guid":"-DnPwIq-c09rJ20QE8N53w","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Metabolización, Vía biliar, Vía renal","guid":"XOS4IJgLZbHX3TlZBsPoww","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"32","text":"Penetración en Bilis (%):","guid":"CNwp1yuqCDeTLLNowKRgxw","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Sin datos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"32","text":"Concentración LCR/Sangre (%):","guid":"wCCzKt6PsxX2RyAbTGVL0A","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• >50%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"32","text":"Niveles Terapéuticos en LCR:","guid":"Mop9XO1vPBZNgrg0dvdPqQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Sí (CID 2009;49:1080)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"32","text":"AUC (µg*hr/mL):","guid":"cA1p_nU5RIMJGddW_nhMTw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• 48 (400 mg po q24h, 0-24 h)","guid":"VHGGcT5gw_Mf4HjGtkl8PQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• 38 (400 mg IV q24h, 0-24 h)","guid":"9dUtUCzqW4dLdWKxNOeDJA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones\\NFarmacológicas\\NMayores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Antiácidos (Al, Mg): ↓ moxifloxacino → Administrar moxi 4 h antes o 8 h después.","guid":"m_vaBfKbNAghc0JlesyF-Q","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Antiarrítmicos (Clase IA/III): ↑ intervalo QT → Evitar coadministración.","guid":"zE53PiSctel61gFWtAJ-gA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Delamanid: ↑ intervalo QT → Evitar coadministración.","guid":"ufcaorW25Op7FZOAPd7--Q","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Didanosina: ↓ moxifloxacino → Administrar moxi 4 h antes o 8 h después.","guid":"9dpLXIrSYH5XU1aShGzoxw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"• Suplementos de hierro: ↓ moxifloxacino → Administrar moxi 4 h antes o 8 h después.","guid":"UckmzTLltkJPxTVRWKbFNw","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"• Insulina: ↑↓ glucemia → Monitorizar.","guid":"lKfHRNIcqNjXzZibJ6QM1A","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"60","text":"• Hipoglucemiantes orales: ↑↓ glucemia → Monitorizar.","guid":"k7Rd1-wGKZZGQXdsQIrfkA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"60","text":"• Osimertinib: ↑ intervalo QT, TdP (BMC Pulm Med 2020;20:181) → Evitar coadministración.","guid":"wtS0c9UR0xURjTeKUqBcEQ","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"60","text":"• Rifampina: ↓ moxifloxacino (Clin Infect Dis 45:1001, 2007) → Monitorizar, ajustar dosis.","guid":"GiW4x-SO8ZhuGvbON-hk0w","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"60","text":"• Warfarina: ↑ warfarina (↑ INR) → Monitorizar INR, ajustar dosis.","guid":"2xqURCd9H5fH7ieGYL0mxQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"60","text":"• Zinc: ↓ moxifloxacino → Administrar moxi 4 h antes o 8 h después.","guid":"l5Cks7Nay_yPrfQI5io0Iw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":71,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Moxifloxacino-2024","id":"map_1165","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Moxifloxacino-2024"}